      <h4>by Sam Moore 1 Comment</h4>
          <p>User research doesn’t have to be a big dollar, corporate initiative. Sam Moore shows how, by paying attention to the people, tools, and work practices within an organization, your team can demonstrate the value of user research on the ground—which will open doors to additional resources in the future.</p>
